sql: SELECT MIN(Lowest), concert.Stadium_ID, Lowest, Theme FROM stadium JOIN singer_in_concert JOIN concert ON concert.Stadium_ID = stadium.Stadium_ID AND concert.concert_ID = singer_in_concert.concert_ID WHERE  Average >= 76 GROUP BY Theme HAVING SUM(stadium.Stadium_ID) = 83 ORDER BY Theme DESC
SELECT x.concert_ID, x.concert_Name FROM concert AS x WHERE  x.concert_ID > 80
SELECT SUM(u.concert_ID), MAX(u.concert_ID), u.Singer_ID FROM singer_in_concert AS u WHERE  u.concert_ID > 46
SELECT AVG(Age), singer_in_concert.Singer_ID FROM singer_in_concert JOIN singer ON singer_in_concert.Singer_ID = singer.Singer_ID WHERE  concert_ID != 0 ORDER BY singer_in_concert.Singer_ID ASC

SELECT concert.concert_ID, Age, concert.concert_ID FROM singer_in_concert JOIN concert JOIN singer ON concert.concert_ID = singer_in_concert.concert_ID AND singer_in_concert.Singer_ID = singer.Singer_ID WHERE Age BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR Theme IN (SELECT Theme FROM concert WHERE  concert_ID > 57) LIMIT 8

SELECT MAX(Age), SUM(concert.concert_ID), Stadium_ID FROM singer_in_concert JOIN concert JOIN singer ON concert.concert_ID = singer_in_concert.concert_ID AND singer_in_concert.Singer_ID = singer.Singer_ID WHERE concert_ID IN (SELECT concert_ID FROM singer_in_concert) GROUP BY Stadium_ID HAVING SUM(Age) >= 67 ORDER BY Stadium_ID DESC
SELECT SUM(concert_ID), Year, Theme FROM concert GROUP BY Theme HAVING COUNT(concert_ID) = 46 ORDER BY Year DESC

SELECT Age, Song_release_year FROM singer_in_concert JOIN concert JOIN singer ON concert.concert_ID = singer_in_concert.concert_ID AND singer_in_concert.Singer_ID = singer.Singer_ID WHERE  concert.concert_ID > 99 GROUP BY Song_release_year HAVING MAX(Age) > 51 ORDER BY Age DESC
SELECT SUM(x.Lowest), COUNT(DISTINCT x.Capacity) FROM stadium AS x WHERE  x.Stadium_ID <= 0
SELECT COUNT(Singer_ID), Age FROM singer WHERE  Singer_ID <= 95 AND Singer_ID NOT IN (SELECT Singer_ID FROM singer AS y WHERE  y.Age != 99) LIMIT 9

SELECT Capacity, concert.Stadium_ID FROM stadium JOIN concert ON concert.Stadium_ID = stadium.Stadium_ID WHERE stadium.Stadium_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR Capacity IN (SELECT Capacity FROM stadium AS k WHERE  k.Capacity <= 68) ORDER BY Capacity ASC
SELECT f.Singer_ID FROM singer AS f WHERE  f.Age >= 12 AND Country NOT IN (SELECT Country FROM singer AS l LIMIT 7) ORDER BY f.Singer_ID ASC
SELECT Singer_ID FROM singer_in_concert WHERE  concert_ID != 53
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Country), Age FROM singer WHERE Song_release_year < (SELECT SUM(Song_release_year) FROM singer WHERE  Singer_ID > 46)

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT singer_in_concert.Singer_ID) FROM singer_in_concert JOIN concert JOIN singer ON concert.concert_ID = singer_in_concert.concert_ID AND singer_in_concert.Singer_ID = singer.Singer_ID WHERE  Age != 95
SELECT concert.Year, f.Stadium_ID FROM concert AS f JOIN concert ON concert.concert_ID = f.concert_ID WHERE  concert.concert_ID > 60 GROUP BY f.Stadium_ID
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT j.Lowest) FROM stadium AS j
SELECT y.concert_ID FROM concert AS y WHERE y.concert_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  y.concert_ID = 89

SELECT m.Singer_ID, singer_in_concert.Singer_ID FROM singer_in_concert AS m JOIN singer_in_concert ON singer_in_concert.concert_ID = m.concert_ID WHERE singer_in_concert.concert_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 LIMIT 3
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT w.Highest), w.Lowest FROM stadium JOIN stadium AS w ON stadium.Stadium_ID = w.Stadium_ID WHERE  w.Stadium_ID <= 90 GROUP BY w.Lowest LIMIT 8
SELECT AVG(Highest) FROM stadium JOIN concert ON concert.Stadium_ID = stadium.Stadium_ID WHERE  Highest = 75
SELECT COUNT(concert_ID), COUNT(DISTINCT concert_ID) FROM concert WHERE concert_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR concert_Name NOT IN (SELECT concert_Name FROM concert AS s WHERE  s.concert_ID != 27) LIMIT 3

SELECT MAX(concert.concert_ID), concert_Name FROM singer_in_concert JOIN concert ON concert.concert_ID = singer_in_concert.concert_ID WHERE  singer_in_concert.concert_ID = 29 GROUP BY concert_Name ORDER BY concert_Name DESC

SELECT Year FROM singer_in_concert JOIN concert ON concert.concert_ID = singer_in_concert.concert_ID WHERE  singer_in_concert.concert_ID < 89 GROUP BY Year HAVING MAX(concert.concert_ID) = 25 ORDER BY Year ASC LIMIT 6
SELECT Singer_ID FROM singer WHERE  Age >= 35 AND Singer_ID IN (SELECT Singer_ID FROM singer AS v WHERE  v.Singer_ID >= 26)
SELECT MAX(concert_ID), MIN(concert_ID) FROM singer_in_concert WHERE concert_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Singer_ID = (SELECT AVG(Singer_ID) FROM singer_in_concert) LIMIT 8
SELECT Age, Singer_ID FROM singer WHERE  Singer_ID > 51
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT f.concert_Name), COUNT(DISTINCT f.Stadium_ID), f.concert_ID FROM concert AS f WHERE f.concert_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Year > (SELECT SUM(Year) FROM concert AS q)

SELECT MIN(concert.concert_ID), singer_in_concert.concert_ID, Average FROM stadium JOIN singer_in_concert JOIN concert JOIN singer ON concert.Stadium_ID = stadium.Stadium_ID AND concert.concert_ID = singer_in_concert.concert_ID AND singer_in_concert.Singer_ID = singer.Singer_ID WHERE stadium.Stadium_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR Song_Name < (SELECT MAX(Song_Name) FROM singer AS h WHERE h.Singer_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10) GROUP BY Average LIMIT 8
SELECT Singer_ID FROM singer_in_concert WHERE concert_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  concert_ID != 89
SELECT MIN(concert.concert_ID) FROM singer_in_concert JOIN concert ON concert.concert_ID = singer_in_concert.concert_ID WHERE Stadium_ID > (SELECT AVG(Stadium_ID) FROM concert WHERE  concert_ID = 94)
SELECT Age, Song_release_year FROM singer_in_concert JOIN singer ON singer_in_concert.Singer_ID = singer.Singer_ID WHERE  Age < 97
